WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.000
Support Admin Watch on
kissasia.cam or kisskh.org

00:02:24.910 --> 00:02:25.980
The evidence report is in.

00:02:27.190 --> 00:02:28.820
The taxi's gear shift at the scene

00:02:29.000 --> 00:02:29.890
was not engaged.

00:02:30.520 --> 00:02:31.610
I went to the scene and noticed

00:02:31.630 --> 00:02:33.010
that the concealed tire marks

00:02:33.280 --> 00:02:34.380
showed the front wheels had

00:02:34.520 --> 00:02:36.060
significantly greater
friction than normal.

00:02:36.240 --> 00:02:37.010
I think the perpetrator

00:02:37.030 --> 00:02:38.100
pushed the car into the lake

00:02:38.400 --> 00:02:39.660
after committing the murder.

00:02:54.840 --> 00:02:56.500
Hello? You need to come quickly.

00:02:57.240 --> 00:02:57.980
I'm at the reservoir

00:02:58.000 --> 00:02:58.780
right now.

00:02:59.150 --> 00:02:59.540
Yes.

00:03:00.520 --> 00:03:00.980
Bad news.

00:03:01.560 --> 00:03:02.100
Something bad...

00:03:02.870 --> 00:03:04.540
Someone's dead.

00:03:06.080 --> 00:03:06.570
Yes.

00:03:08.000 --> 00:03:08.570
I'll wait here.

00:03:09.000 --> 00:03:09.570
I'll wait.

00:04:15.520 --> 00:04:16.460
How's Ms. Zhu now?

00:04:17.480 --> 00:04:18.100
She's okay.

00:04:25.160 --> 00:04:25.490
Zhu!

00:04:25.950 --> 00:04:26.250
Hey, Wan!

00:04:26.510 --> 00:04:27.100
You got hurt?

00:04:27.720 --> 00:04:28.660
It's nothing. Let's go.

00:04:28.920 --> 00:04:29.660
What do you mean?

00:04:29.720 --> 00:04:30.340
We're already here.

00:04:30.560 --> 00:04:31.050
Get a CT scan

00:04:31.070 --> 00:04:31.850
and a full check-up.

00:04:32.630 --> 00:04:33.780
I've asked for a day off for you.

00:04:34.190 --> 00:04:34.540
Come on!

00:04:34.560 --> 00:04:35.340
I'm really fine.

00:04:35.480 --> 00:04:35.930
Let's go.

00:04:36.800 --> 00:04:37.410
Zhu Qingyue!

00:04:42.430 --> 00:04:43.730
Huatao specifically asked me

00:04:43.750 --> 00:04:44.850
to take good care of you

00:04:44.870 --> 00:04:45.700
when he passed away.

00:04:46.070 --> 00:04:47.050
And now you won't even

00:04:47.070 --> 00:04:47.490
listen to me?

00:04:48.070 --> 00:04:48.900
Can we skip him?

00:04:52.270 --> 00:04:53.290
Go get a proper check-up later.

00:04:54.190 --> 00:04:54.580
Wan,

00:04:55.190 --> 00:04:56.140
I saw the suspect from the

00:04:56.160 --> 00:04:56.580
Li Yiqi case.

00:05:08.070 --> 00:05:08.730
She didn't rest?

00:06:10.120 --> 00:06:11.340
We've traced the license plate.

00:06:11.630 --> 00:06:13.140
It's B53617,

00:06:13.560 --> 00:06:14.610
but it's fake.

00:06:15.040 --> 00:06:16.930
Yet traffic police tracked it entering

00:06:17.070 --> 00:06:18.810
the Fenglin Ducheng
Community last night,

00:06:19.040 --> 00:06:20.370
where it stayed for an hour.

00:06:21.360 --> 00:06:22.250
Coincidentally,

00:06:22.750 --> 00:06:24.340
a fatal fall occurred in the community

00:06:24.480 --> 00:06:25.410
at the exact same time.

00:06:26.070 --> 00:06:27.170
That person went there

00:06:27.480 --> 00:06:28.540
that night to find Wang Chen.

00:06:28.800 --> 00:06:30.170
They said this medicine

00:06:30.920 --> 00:06:32.140
gave us the courage to jump.

00:06:37.270 --> 00:06:37.660
Mr. Qi,

00:06:38.510 --> 00:06:39.540
Wang Chen's blood test report

00:06:39.560 --> 00:06:40.020
is out.

00:06:40.160 --> 00:06:41.290
Traces of an anesthetic were found.

00:07:08.600 --> 00:07:09.410
What... what is this?

00:07:09.920 --> 00:07:10.290
What?

00:07:10.310 --> 00:07:10.850
What's so heavy?

00:07:11.430 --> 00:07:11.850
A box?

00:07:12.600 --> 00:07:13.170
Help me out.

00:07:13.430 --> 00:07:13.810
Come on!

00:07:14.310 --> 00:07:14.780
Just leave it.

00:07:14.870 --> 00:07:15.340
Let me see.

00:07:21.310 --> 00:07:21.900
It's a woman!

00:07:23.190 --> 00:07:23.810
Call the police!

00:07:24.120 --> 00:07:24.700
Call the police!

00:07:37.000 --> 00:07:37.540
How did it go?

00:07:37.950 --> 00:07:38.220
Ning,

00:07:38.360 --> 00:07:38.700
the boss

00:07:38.720 --> 00:07:39.980
says no strangers appeared.

00:07:40.430 --> 00:07:40.850
Ask them.

00:07:41.070 --> 00:07:41.580
Got it.

00:07:42.560 --> 00:07:43.020
Ning,

00:07:44.000 --> 00:07:45.580
I've asked several households too.

00:07:45.680 --> 00:07:46.900
Nothing so far.

00:07:47.390 --> 00:07:48.140
Okay, I understand.

00:07:51.390 --> 00:07:52.020
Make way.

00:07:52.830 --> 00:07:53.700
Everyone, please make way.

00:07:53.950 --> 00:07:54.460
Mr. Han.

00:08:00.600 --> 00:08:01.220
This body

00:08:01.310 --> 00:08:02.340
was found in a trash bin

00:08:02.360 --> 00:08:03.490
by those two sanitation workers.

00:08:04.360 --> 00:08:05.250
I just looked around;

00:08:05.430 --> 00:08:06.540
there's no security camera here.

00:08:09.190 --> 00:08:09.610
How is it?

00:08:09.920 --> 00:08:10.540
The victim is

00:08:10.600 --> 00:08:11.540
a young woman.

00:08:11.830 --> 00:08:13.220
Apart from facial disfigurement,

00:08:13.390 --> 00:08:14.610
her fingerprints are worn off.

00:08:15.920 --> 00:08:16.340
Mr. Han,

00:08:16.510 --> 00:08:17.340
I don't understand why

00:08:17.430 --> 00:08:18.850
there are so many homicide cases lately?

00:08:19.240 --> 00:08:20.220
I found something strange.

00:08:39.960 --> 00:08:40.700
Time of death is

00:08:40.720 --> 00:08:41.940
estimated to be about two days ago,

00:08:42.840 --> 00:08:44.180
between 9 and 11 PM.

00:08:45.270 --> 00:08:45.650
Mr. Han.

00:08:45.960 --> 00:08:46.460
How did it go?

00:08:47.200 --> 00:08:48.060
The deceased is female,

00:08:48.200 --> 00:08:49.100
approximately 5'41'' tall,

00:08:49.120 --> 00:08:50.130
weighing around 110 pounds.

00:08:50.600 --> 00:08:51.370
Judging from the fusion

00:08:51.510 --> 00:08:52.730
of the epiphyseal lines in the long

00:08:52.960 --> 00:08:54.610
bones and the symphyseal
surface of the pubis,

00:08:55.000 --> 00:08:55.730
the estimated age

00:08:55.910 --> 00:08:57.130
is between 29

00:08:57.150 --> 00:08:58.420
and 32.

00:08:58.750 --> 00:08:59.490
No childbirth history.

00:08:59.750 --> 00:09:00.250
No signs of

00:09:00.270 --> 00:09:01.180
sexual assault before death.

00:09:02.000 --> 00:09:03.010
We found some food residue

00:09:03.030 --> 00:09:04.580
in the deceased's stomach:

00:09:04.630 --> 00:09:06.220
beef, bread, and broccoli.

00:09:06.480 --> 00:09:06.980
The blood

00:09:07.000 --> 00:09:07.890
contained alcohol.

00:09:08.480 --> 00:09:10.010
Based on several post-mortem indicators

00:09:10.360 --> 00:09:11.730
and the stomach contents,

00:09:11.750 --> 00:09:12.460
the estimated time

00:09:12.720 --> 00:09:13.610
of death is

00:09:13.720 --> 00:09:15.300
about two days ago,

00:09:15.390 --> 00:09:16.730
between 9 and 11 PM.

00:09:17.150 --> 00:09:18.890
Cause of death is massive hemorrhage.

00:09:19.320 --> 00:09:20.010
The fatal wound is to

00:09:21.030 --> 00:09:21.730
the carotid artery.

00:09:21.910 --> 00:09:22.940
What kind of weapon caused it?

00:09:23.750 --> 00:09:25.340
The shape of the weapon
is very peculiar,

00:09:26.030 --> 00:09:26.890
resembling

00:09:27.080 --> 00:09:28.770
a triangular, blade-like object.

00:09:29.240 --> 00:09:30.730
The wound is on the right side.

00:09:31.440 --> 00:09:32.490
The perpetrator is left-handed.

00:09:33.150 --> 00:09:33.730
Very likely.

00:09:34.440 --> 00:09:35.060
What about the DNA?

00:09:35.550 --> 00:09:36.370
No matches found

00:09:36.390 --> 00:09:37.340
among missing persons.

00:09:40.120 --> 00:09:41.460
So we can only start

00:09:41.870 --> 00:09:43.100
investigating with that tattoo

00:09:43.120 --> 00:09:44.100
on her lower back.

00:09:46.630 --> 00:09:47.420
I remember something.

00:09:47.670 --> 00:09:48.980
I think I recall an unsolved case.

00:09:49.480 --> 00:09:50.730
The wounds on the victim were

00:09:51.360 --> 00:09:52.180
very similar to hers.

00:09:52.910 --> 00:09:53.770
Fourteen years ago,

00:09:53.960 --> 00:09:55.580
a murder occurred in Lijia Town.

00:09:56.550 --> 00:09:57.490
The victim was a 19-year-old

00:09:57.510 --> 00:09:58.250
female college girl.

00:09:58.440 --> 00:09:59.700
The perpetrator was never found.

00:09:59.910 --> 00:10:01.130
The officers at the time deduced the

00:10:01.270 --> 00:10:02.220
weapon was a fountain pen.

00:10:03.870 --> 00:10:05.250
Was the weapon found at the scene?

00:10:05.960 --> 00:10:06.420
No.

00:10:07.840 --> 00:10:08.490
Is there

00:10:09.000 --> 00:10:10.130
more information on this case?

00:10:10.480 --> 00:10:11.370
For more information,

00:10:11.440 --> 00:10:12.650
we'll need to go back to the scene

00:10:12.910 --> 00:10:14.100
and find the detectives of the case

00:10:14.320 --> 00:10:15.220
to get the basic details.

00:10:16.960 --> 00:10:17.890
Do you think these two cases

00:10:17.910 --> 00:10:18.700
are connected?

00:10:20.720 --> 00:10:21.940
Judging from the wounds,

00:10:22.840 --> 00:10:23.610
they are very similar.

00:10:24.200 --> 00:10:25.180
But to determine

00:10:25.270 --> 00:10:26.850
if the perpetrator's methods
are consistent,

00:10:27.790 --> 00:10:28.770
we need more information.

00:10:29.790 --> 00:10:30.100
Alright.

00:10:30.240 --> 00:10:30.730
Ms. Zhu,

00:10:30.840 --> 00:10:32.700
you follow up on the tattoo lead.

00:10:33.240 --> 00:10:34.100
We'll go to Lijia Town.

00:10:47.360 --> 00:10:47.850
Hello, Mr. Han!

00:10:48.480 --> 00:10:48.890
Mr. Li.

00:10:49.030 --> 00:10:49.770
You must be Mr. Qi!

00:10:49.870 --> 00:10:50.250
Hello.

00:10:50.390 --> 00:10:50.770
Hi.

00:10:51.320 --> 00:10:52.220
For the case you mentioned,

00:10:52.390 --> 00:10:53.460
we've got the materials ready.

00:10:53.960 --> 00:10:54.580
Let's talk inside.

00:10:55.000 --> 00:10:55.220
Okay.

00:10:55.240 --> 00:10:55.490
Come in.

00:10:59.480 --> 00:11:00.580
Here, have some tea.

00:11:01.510 --> 00:11:01.820
Thanks.

00:11:05.320 --> 00:11:06.890
This case you mentioned

00:11:07.200 --> 00:11:08.890
caused quite a stir

00:11:09.390 --> 00:11:11.250
in our town back then.

00:11:11.720 --> 00:11:12.460
Tell us about it.

00:11:13.630 --> 00:11:16.580
The deceased was named Fan Jiangxue.

00:11:17.080 --> 00:11:18.730
She was raised

00:11:19.150 --> 00:11:20.580
by her grandmother.

00:11:21.270 --> 00:11:23.530
We all watched her grow up.

00:11:24.080 --> 00:11:26.100
She loved painting since she was a child

00:11:26.720 --> 00:11:28.700
and often went to the
back mountain to sketch.

00:11:29.200 --> 00:11:30.370
On the day of the incident,

00:11:31.440 --> 00:11:32.820
the whole town was in chaos.

00:11:33.030 --> 00:11:33.890
Everything

00:11:34.270 --> 00:11:35.650
was thrown into disarray.

00:11:36.320 --> 00:11:37.650
No suspect was caught back then?

00:11:38.270 --> 00:11:39.730
Our town

00:11:40.630 --> 00:11:41.770
had never seen

00:11:41.790 --> 00:11:43.130
such a brutal case.

00:11:43.550 --> 00:11:45.130
Plus, over a decade ago,

00:11:45.600 --> 00:11:47.940
investigative methods
weren't as advanced.

00:11:48.440 --> 00:11:49.420
I was wondering

00:11:49.790 --> 00:11:51.100
if this case would

00:11:51.360 --> 00:11:52.650
remain unsolved

00:11:53.270 --> 00:11:53.980
until my retirement.

00:11:57.080 --> 00:11:59.130
For the body you found,

00:11:59.790 --> 00:12:02.580
do the wounds really match Jiangxue's?

00:12:03.750 --> 00:12:06.130
Could the killer be the same person?

00:12:06.910 --> 00:12:07.850
It's not certain yet.

00:12:17.270 --> 00:12:18.250
This person is...?

00:12:20.390 --> 00:12:21.220
This girl

00:12:21.320 --> 00:12:22.650
is named Hu Jie.

00:12:23.360 --> 00:12:25.700
She grew up with Jiangxue.

00:12:26.120 --> 00:12:27.770
Jiangxue's family was poor,

00:12:28.080 --> 00:12:29.490
but Hu Jie was

00:12:29.510 --> 00:12:30.300
kind-hearted and

00:12:30.550 --> 00:12:31.180
didn't despise her.

00:12:31.630 --> 00:12:32.300
The two of them

00:12:32.600 --> 00:12:34.220
often went up the mountain
to paint together.

00:12:35.440 --> 00:12:36.610
Was this Hu Jie present at

00:12:36.960 --> 00:12:37.850
the time of the incident?

00:12:38.550 --> 00:12:41.060
She said she had a cold and stayed

00:12:41.440 --> 00:12:42.130
home that day.

00:12:42.480 --> 00:12:43.300
So she wasn't there.

00:12:44.240 --> 00:12:45.300
I'm glad she didn't go.

00:12:45.670 --> 00:12:46.370
If she had,

00:12:46.550 --> 00:12:48.250
she might have been killed too.

00:12:50.320 --> 00:12:51.180
Does she live in town now?

00:12:51.550 --> 00:12:52.250
Can we see her?

00:12:53.360 --> 00:12:55.250
Since Jiangxue's case had
remained unsolved,

00:12:55.600 --> 00:12:57.890
the whole town was on edge.

00:12:58.120 --> 00:12:59.460
Many people moved away.

00:12:59.960 --> 00:13:01.610
As for Hu Jie, I heard

00:13:01.840 --> 00:13:02.490
her parents

00:13:03.030 --> 00:13:04.460
arranged for her to study abroad.

00:13:09.390 --> 00:13:09.940
Ms. Zhu,

00:13:11.150 --> 00:13:12.220
I've checked a few tattoo shops

00:13:12.320 --> 00:13:13.580
but found no lead.

00:13:14.030 --> 00:13:14.530
Keep looking.

00:13:14.600 --> 00:13:15.100
Okay.

00:13:18.870 --> 00:13:20.300
Ms. Zhu, I found something!

00:13:24.550 --> 00:13:25.180
I found a girl

00:13:25.200 --> 00:13:26.530
with the exact same tattoo

00:13:26.720 --> 00:13:27.420
in a video posted

00:13:27.440 --> 00:13:28.530
by an online blogger.

00:13:29.270 --> 00:13:29.610
Yes,

00:13:30.030 --> 00:13:30.940
that's the one!

00:13:31.270 --> 00:13:32.420
It's identical to the Jane Doe's;

00:13:32.440 --> 00:13:33.250
so is the location!

00:13:33.630 --> 00:13:34.530
She went abroad

00:13:34.550 --> 00:13:35.370
to study art when

00:13:35.390 --> 00:13:36.060
she was a teenager

00:13:36.240 --> 00:13:37.010
and has returned lately.

00:13:37.550 --> 00:13:38.300
What's her name?

00:13:38.630 --> 00:13:39.220
Don't know yet.

00:13:39.670 --> 00:13:40.700
I only know her username.

00:13:41.550 --> 00:13:42.300
Confirm her identity

00:13:42.320 --> 00:13:43.220
as soon as possible.

00:13:43.790 --> 00:13:44.180
Got it.

00:13:44.870 --> 00:13:45.700
She was abroad.

00:13:45.720 --> 00:13:46.650
Figures we can't track her.

00:13:47.080 --> 00:13:48.340
Good job, Su!

00:13:52.480 --> 00:13:53.700
Her friend was killed the same day

00:13:53.720 --> 00:13:54.650
she happened to be absent.

00:13:55.000 --> 00:13:55.610
After that,

00:13:55.630 --> 00:13:56.370
she went abroad.

00:13:56.440 --> 00:13:57.490
Hu Jie is definitely suspicious.

00:13:57.870 --> 00:13:59.010
Age-wise,

00:13:59.360 --> 00:14:00.940
she's also close to the Jane Doe.

00:14:04.080 --> 00:14:04.420
Hello?

00:14:05.000 --> 00:14:05.610
Hello, Mr. Han.

00:14:05.910 --> 00:14:06.730
We found a girl

00:14:06.750 --> 00:14:07.650
online with

00:14:07.720 --> 00:14:08.580
a tattoo identical

00:14:08.600 --> 00:14:10.180
to the Jane Doe's.

00:14:10.870 --> 00:14:11.490
(We're still)

00:14:11.510 --> 00:14:12.250
(checking her ID.)

00:14:12.910 --> 00:14:13.820
I'll send you the photo.

00:14:14.840 --> 00:14:15.220
Su,

00:14:16.080 --> 00:14:16.610
send to Mr. Han.

00:14:16.790 --> 00:14:17.130
Okay.

00:14:24.960 --> 00:14:25.700
It's Hu Jie.

00:14:28.510 --> 00:14:28.980
This girl is

00:14:29.000 --> 00:14:30.730
the friend of the
deceased from Lijia Town.

00:14:30.750 --> 00:14:31.420
Her name is Hu Jie.

00:14:31.840 --> 00:14:32.940
I'll send you Hu Jie's

00:14:32.960 --> 00:14:33.610
information.

00:14:34.150 --> 00:14:34.980
Find her family to

00:14:35.320 --> 00:14:36.060
compare DNA and

00:14:36.080 --> 00:14:36.650
confirm ID.

00:14:37.270 --> 00:14:37.530
Okay.

00:14:54.390 --> 00:14:54.850
Hello.

00:14:56.240 --> 00:14:56.980
This cabin

00:14:57.360 --> 00:14:59.340
was originally used as a rest stop

00:14:59.720 --> 00:15:00.730
for nearby forest rangers.

00:15:01.390 --> 00:15:03.650
Over time, fewer people came,

00:15:04.440 --> 00:15:04.980
so

00:15:05.600 --> 00:15:06.490
it was abandoned.

00:15:07.510 --> 00:15:08.180
Come take a look.

00:15:13.960 --> 00:15:14.220
Come on.

00:15:17.600 --> 00:15:19.300
Jiangxue and Hu Jie

00:15:19.480 --> 00:15:20.180
used to

00:15:20.510 --> 00:15:22.060
come here to play a lot.

00:15:23.200 --> 00:15:23.980
However,

00:15:24.440 --> 00:15:26.700
after what happened to Jiangxue,

00:15:26.720 --> 00:15:28.890
no one dared to come in anymore.

00:15:31.630 --> 00:15:32.220
Be careful.

00:15:32.910 --> 00:15:33.250
It's fine.

00:15:33.550 --> 00:15:35.420
Some kids in town

00:15:35.600 --> 00:15:36.820
call this place the haunted house

00:15:38.000 --> 00:15:38.820
and come exploring.

00:15:40.360 --> 00:15:41.010
Occasionally,

00:15:41.270 --> 00:15:42.530
a few mischievous kids

00:15:42.630 --> 00:15:43.460
come up here.

00:15:44.840 --> 00:15:45.580
Watch your steps.

00:15:46.270 --> 00:15:46.650
Over here.

00:16:03.270 --> 00:16:04.650
This was the crime scene back then.

00:16:05.270 --> 00:16:06.370
The body was right there.

00:16:24.120 --> 00:16:24.650
Here?

00:16:24.720 --> 00:16:25.220
Yes.

00:16:40.910 --> 00:16:42.820
The forensic examiner
back then concluded

00:16:43.000 --> 00:16:44.820
that the cause of death
was excessive blood loss

00:16:45.000 --> 00:16:46.370
after the carotid artery was pierced;

00:16:46.790 --> 00:16:47.850
the weapon was a fountain pen,

00:16:47.910 --> 00:16:49.370
but it wasn't found

00:16:49.390 --> 00:16:50.420
at the scene.

00:16:50.960 --> 00:16:52.370
How do you know it was a fountain pen?

00:16:53.200 --> 00:16:54.340
The wound shape matched,

00:16:54.840 --> 00:16:56.980
and fountain pen ink was
found in the wound.

00:17:05.030 --> 00:17:06.050
We also found

00:17:06.070 --> 00:17:06.900
an easel at the scene.

00:17:07.440 --> 00:17:08.090
Next to Fan Jiangxue

00:17:08.110 --> 00:17:09.290
was a fountain pen

00:17:10.590 --> 00:17:12.530
with only her own fingerprints,

00:17:13.440 --> 00:17:14.290
but no blood.

00:17:15.310 --> 00:17:15.700
Also,

00:17:15.720 --> 00:17:16.730
we noticed that someone

00:17:16.960 --> 00:17:18.220
had obviously cleaned the scene.

00:17:18.680 --> 00:17:19.860
Fingerprints, footprints,

00:17:20.200 --> 00:17:20.860
all gone.

00:17:21.310 --> 00:17:23.140
Finally, we found a strand of hair.

00:17:23.880 --> 00:17:25.460
The shape of the weapon
is very peculiar,

00:17:26.110 --> 00:17:27.010
resembling

00:17:27.200 --> 00:17:28.900
a triangular, blade-like object.

00:17:57.720 --> 00:17:59.700
How was the perpetrator's method

00:18:00.270 --> 00:18:01.180
determined back then?

00:18:01.510 --> 00:18:02.860
The wound surface is

00:18:02.880 --> 00:18:04.140
on the right side of the neck.

00:18:04.400 --> 00:18:06.980
When analyzing the entry
wound and the force applied,

00:18:07.440 --> 00:18:09.330
it should be a forward diagonal stab.

00:18:10.000 --> 00:18:12.290
But if the right hand
was used, the killer

00:18:12.920 --> 00:18:14.330
could only stab with a backhand,

00:18:14.790 --> 00:18:15.980
which would be

00:18:16.310 --> 00:18:17.420
extremely awkward.

00:18:17.640 --> 00:18:19.980
However, if the left hand was used,

00:18:20.240 --> 00:18:21.250
there would be no such problem.

00:18:23.720 --> 00:18:24.380
So,

00:18:25.030 --> 00:18:26.290
the perpetrator is left-handed.

00:18:27.110 --> 00:18:27.380
Correct.

00:18:27.920 --> 00:18:28.420
That was

00:18:28.920 --> 00:18:30.050
our judgment back then.

00:18:32.030 --> 00:18:33.250
What was the result

00:18:33.640 --> 00:18:34.460
of the hair comparison?

00:18:35.270 --> 00:18:36.050
That hair was

00:18:36.400 --> 00:18:37.180
a broken strand,

00:18:37.400 --> 00:18:38.660
completely lacking the follicle.

00:18:39.000 --> 00:18:39.660
So,

00:18:40.070 --> 00:18:41.380
it couldn't be used for identification.

00:18:41.880 --> 00:18:42.490
We only knew

00:18:42.790 --> 00:18:44.050
it wasn't Fan Jiangxue's.

00:18:56.830 --> 00:18:58.050
There was only an easel at the scene,

00:18:58.350 --> 00:18:59.330
but no painting was found.

00:19:00.240 --> 00:19:01.010
We found it

00:19:01.510 --> 00:19:02.460
quite puzzling as well.

00:19:02.960 --> 00:19:04.290
We thought it might have been blown away

00:19:04.310 --> 00:19:04.770
or something.

00:19:04.960 --> 00:19:07.620
So we had people search

00:19:07.880 --> 00:19:08.530
the entire area,

00:19:08.960 --> 00:19:09.900
but found no painting.

00:19:10.510 --> 00:19:11.940
The killer probably left evidence on it,

00:19:12.310 --> 00:19:13.090
so they took it away.

00:19:14.270 --> 00:19:14.980
No idea.

00:19:49.880 --> 00:19:50.330
Ms. Zhu,

00:19:51.160 --> 00:19:51.900
we've contacted

00:19:51.920 --> 00:19:52.700
Hu Jie's parents.

00:19:53.000 --> 00:19:54.290
They are currently abroad.

00:19:55.590 --> 00:19:56.250
They said

00:19:56.270 --> 00:19:57.420
Hu Jie returned several months ago.

00:19:58.030 --> 00:19:58.730
But we checked her

00:19:58.750 --> 00:19:59.770
communication records.

00:19:59.830 --> 00:20:00.660
Her phone number is an

00:20:00.680 --> 00:20:01.290
Australian number.

00:20:01.920 --> 00:20:02.770
There's currently no

00:20:02.790 --> 00:20:03.730
effective information.

00:20:04.590 --> 00:20:06.290
This is the cleaning lady from her home.

00:20:06.750 --> 00:20:07.570
She let us in.

00:20:11.920 --> 00:20:12.330
Ms. Zhu.

00:20:13.590 --> 00:20:14.180
Hi, ma'am.

00:20:14.920 --> 00:20:15.380
Hello.

00:20:15.680 --> 00:20:16.530
Let's sit and talk.

00:20:17.790 --> 00:20:18.140
Here.

00:20:19.110 --> 00:20:19.620
Please, ma'am.

00:20:20.790 --> 00:20:22.660
I'll just ask you a few
simple questions.

00:20:24.200 --> 00:20:25.460
When was the last time

00:20:25.480 --> 00:20:26.140
you saw Hu Jie?

00:20:26.440 --> 00:20:28.220
When I came to clean
the day before yesterday.

00:20:29.510 --> 00:20:30.490
What time did you arrive?

00:20:31.350 --> 00:20:32.940
Around 2 PM.

00:20:34.160 --> 00:20:35.860
Was Hu Jie home at that time?

00:20:36.240 --> 00:20:36.860
Yes.

00:20:37.960 --> 00:20:39.770
I started cleaning in the afternoon

00:20:39.920 --> 00:20:41.330
and left around 6 PM.

00:20:41.590 --> 00:20:42.250
Ms. Hu

00:20:42.270 --> 00:20:43.860
went out a little after 5 PM.

00:20:44.750 --> 00:20:46.700
It seemed like she had
a dinner appointment.

00:21:01.550 --> 00:21:02.620
She got a call

00:21:02.830 --> 00:21:04.050
and left in a hurry.

00:21:05.030 --> 00:21:05.660
Do you know who

00:21:05.720 --> 00:21:06.700
she was meeting for dinner?

00:21:07.310 --> 00:21:08.860
I only heard her on the phone,

00:21:09.240 --> 00:21:10.140
but don't know who it was.

00:21:11.790 --> 00:21:12.090
Okay,

00:21:12.640 --> 00:21:13.460
thank you.

00:21:13.880 --> 00:21:14.290
Hui,

00:21:14.920 --> 00:21:16.180
take a statement from her

00:21:16.350 --> 00:21:17.250
and then escort her home.

00:21:17.880 --> 00:21:18.220
Got it.

00:21:18.440 --> 00:21:19.290
We'll contact you again

00:21:19.310 --> 00:21:20.250
if we need anything later.

00:21:20.790 --> 00:21:21.140
Okay.

00:21:21.160 --> 00:21:21.490
Thank you.

00:21:22.000 --> 00:21:22.490
Thanks.

00:21:31.720 --> 00:21:32.090
Ms. Zhu,

00:21:33.270 --> 00:21:34.140
come take a look at this.

00:21:35.030 --> 00:21:36.250
She must have been copying this one.

00:21:59.400 --> 00:22:00.290
I've noticed something.

00:22:00.720 --> 00:22:01.770
All her paintings

00:22:01.790 --> 00:22:02.660
have the initial "H".

00:22:03.030 --> 00:22:04.090
It's likely her signature.

00:22:04.440 --> 00:22:05.490
Only this one doesn't.

00:22:15.640 --> 00:22:16.330
This painting

00:22:16.680 --> 00:22:17.620
might not be hers.

00:22:18.400 --> 00:22:19.420
Take all these back

00:22:19.680 --> 00:22:20.180
for comparison.

00:22:20.680 --> 00:22:21.660
Okay. I'll go call them.

00:22:25.270 --> 00:22:25.730
Gao Yuan,

00:22:26.000 --> 00:22:26.620
any findings?

00:22:27.070 --> 00:22:27.460
Ms. Zhu,

00:22:28.310 --> 00:22:29.180
we just discovered several

00:22:29.200 --> 00:22:29.770
fingerprints.

00:22:29.960 --> 00:22:30.770
Here's a hair strand.

00:22:31.200 --> 00:22:32.220
We'll test them to see if they

00:22:32.480 --> 00:22:33.090
belong to Hu Jie

00:22:33.110 --> 00:22:33.810
or someone else.

00:22:34.830 --> 00:22:35.220
Okay.

00:22:56.030 --> 00:22:56.490
Gao Yuan,

00:22:57.640 --> 00:22:58.860
look, there are bloodstains.

00:23:30.830 --> 00:23:31.810
Ms. Zhu, we found something.

00:23:36.510 --> 00:23:37.810
A large number of wiped bloodstains

00:23:37.960 --> 00:23:39.180
were also found in the bathroom.

00:23:40.920 --> 00:23:41.490
Could this be the

00:23:41.510 --> 00:23:43.090
primary crime scene
where Hu Jie was killed?

00:23:51.920 --> 00:23:52.330
Got it.

00:23:55.240 --> 00:23:56.660
The Jane Doe is confirmed to be Hu Jie.

00:23:56.830 --> 00:23:58.330
The crime scene is her home.

00:24:05.240 --> 00:24:06.420
I've already requested to transfer

00:24:06.830 --> 00:24:07.620
the materials from

00:24:07.750 --> 00:24:09.050
the Fan Jiangxue case to our department.

00:24:09.160 --> 00:24:10.980
According to what Xiaoxi has found,

00:24:11.270 --> 00:24:11.860
Hu Jie

00:24:12.200 --> 00:24:12.940
is now

00:24:12.960 --> 00:24:13.810
a professional painter.

00:24:14.480 --> 00:24:15.460
I'll ask the Director

00:24:16.030 --> 00:24:16.940
to help search for

00:24:18.070 --> 00:24:19.530
any paintings

00:24:19.590 --> 00:24:20.730
Fan Jiangxue did back then.

00:24:21.070 --> 00:24:22.380
We can bring them for comparison

00:24:22.640 --> 00:24:23.940
to see if there are new clues

00:24:24.240 --> 00:24:25.290
to help us find

00:24:25.400 --> 00:24:26.290
the missing painting.

00:24:52.960 --> 00:24:53.380
Han Feng,

00:24:55.920 --> 00:24:57.250
have we identified the killer

00:24:57.350 --> 00:24:57.860
of Li Yiqi?

00:24:59.200 --> 00:25:00.090
Wan is on it.

00:25:02.550 --> 00:25:04.050
The killer is related to
the "Diamond" case.

00:25:05.160 --> 00:25:05.940
We are police officers;

00:25:06.000 --> 00:25:06.770
we need evidence.

00:25:21.680 --> 00:25:22.420
In the Jiangxue case,

00:25:22.440 --> 00:25:23.860
the hair strand without

00:25:24.160 --> 00:25:25.220
a follicle found back then is

00:25:25.240 --> 00:25:25.980
called the hair shaft.

00:25:26.590 --> 00:25:27.490
The follicle

00:25:28.000 --> 00:25:28.940
contains nuclear DNA,

00:25:29.160 --> 00:25:30.900
but the hair shaft does not.

00:25:31.550 --> 00:25:32.770
So that strand of hair

00:25:33.200 --> 00:25:34.490
wasn't much help in solving

00:25:34.960 --> 00:25:35.460
the case.

00:25:37.400 --> 00:25:39.140
After Fan Jiangxue was killed,

00:25:39.310 --> 00:25:40.660
Hu Jie left Lijia Town

00:25:40.720 --> 00:25:41.330
and went abroad.

00:25:42.030 --> 00:25:43.770
Fourteen years later, Hu Jie returned,

00:25:44.160 --> 00:25:45.620
and within a few months she was killed.

00:25:46.270 --> 00:25:47.660
The perpetrator's method

00:25:48.030 --> 00:25:49.050
is consistent with the method

00:25:49.070 --> 00:25:50.220
used to kill Fan Jiangxue.

00:25:50.790 --> 00:25:52.090
Can we infer

00:25:52.270 --> 00:25:53.660
the perpetrator might
be the same person?

00:25:57.480 --> 00:25:58.290
Another connection is

00:25:58.480 --> 00:25:59.380
these paintings.

00:26:00.000 --> 00:26:02.050
This one was found at Hu Jie's home.

00:26:02.920 --> 00:26:03.980
This one

00:26:04.000 --> 00:26:05.140
was found in Fan Jiangxue's

00:26:05.160 --> 00:26:05.730
file.

00:26:05.920 --> 00:26:06.530
They both depict

00:26:06.550 --> 00:26:07.050
the same place.

00:26:07.240 --> 00:26:08.420
Ten years apart, not much

00:26:08.680 --> 00:26:09.290
difference.

00:26:12.240 --> 00:26:13.050
This painting,

00:26:13.510 --> 00:26:14.140
although also left

00:26:14.160 --> 00:26:15.250
at Hu Jie's home,

00:26:15.310 --> 00:26:16.010
doesn't

00:26:16.480 --> 00:26:17.660
have Hu Jie's signature.

00:26:18.070 --> 00:26:18.980
And this one's

00:26:19.400 --> 00:26:20.530
paper is obviously yellowed.

00:26:20.750 --> 00:26:21.730
It should be an old painting.

00:26:22.070 --> 00:26:22.900
Could it possibly be the

00:26:22.920 --> 00:26:23.860
one missing from the scene?

00:26:24.790 --> 00:26:26.090
This requires further appraisal

00:26:26.110 --> 00:26:26.810
to know.

00:26:27.350 --> 00:26:28.490
Currently, we only know

00:26:29.200 --> 00:26:30.050
that besides

00:26:30.480 --> 00:26:31.220
Fan Jiangxue's

00:26:31.240 --> 00:26:32.570
and Hu Jie's fingerprints, it also

00:26:32.960 --> 00:26:34.090
bears someone else's prints.

00:26:35.270 --> 00:26:35.730
Su,

00:26:36.270 --> 00:26:37.250
find a professional appraiser

00:26:37.270 --> 00:26:38.140
to determine

00:26:38.400 --> 00:26:40.010
whether this painting
was done by Hu Jie

00:26:40.030 --> 00:26:40.810
or Fan Jiangxue,

00:26:40.920 --> 00:26:41.730
or by a third person.

00:26:42.590 --> 00:26:43.730
Perhaps solving this mystery

00:26:44.110 --> 00:26:44.940
can help us find

00:26:44.960 --> 00:26:45.900
the truth behind

00:26:46.110 --> 00:26:46.860
Fan Jiangxue's murder.

00:26:47.110 --> 00:26:48.180
Okay, I'll handle it later.

00:26:49.270 --> 00:26:49.900
Oh, Gao Yuan, have

00:26:50.880 --> 00:26:52.090
you got the fingerprint match results

00:26:52.200 --> 00:26:52.900
from Hu Jie's?

00:26:53.240 --> 00:26:54.090
We didn't find

00:26:54.110 --> 00:26:54.900
a suitable match in the

00:26:54.920 --> 00:26:55.620
fingerprint database.

00:26:55.790 --> 00:26:57.180
We're still investigating

00:26:57.200 --> 00:26:58.530
who Hu Jie went to meet before

00:26:58.550 --> 00:26:59.090
her death.

00:26:59.350 --> 00:27:00.180
Now we can only judge,

00:27:00.200 --> 00:27:01.530
based on the food residue like beef

00:27:01.550 --> 00:27:02.530
steak in her stomach,

00:27:02.680 --> 00:27:03.220
that she likely

00:27:03.240 --> 00:27:04.380
dined at a Western restaurant.

00:27:04.790 --> 00:27:05.530
Alright, Ms. Zhu.

00:27:05.790 --> 00:27:06.980
You continue investigating Hu Jie.

00:27:07.590 --> 00:27:08.620
We'll look

00:27:08.880 --> 00:27:09.700
into the paintings.

00:27:10.720 --> 00:27:11.900
Xiaoxi, keep checking the footage.

00:27:12.160 --> 00:27:12.530
Okay.

00:27:17.400 --> 00:27:18.180
These three paintings

00:27:18.480 --> 00:27:19.620
were from three different people.

00:27:19.920 --> 00:27:20.380
These two were

00:27:20.400 --> 00:27:21.380
also not from the same person?

00:27:21.960 --> 00:27:23.530
Because the unsigned painting

00:27:23.640 --> 00:27:24.940
used a fountain pen nib

00:27:25.000 --> 00:27:26.220
with a reverse oblique cut,

00:27:26.510 --> 00:27:28.090
while Fan Jiangxue's painting

00:27:28.480 --> 00:27:29.420
used a standard nib.

00:27:30.000 --> 00:27:31.330
Reverse oblique nibs

00:27:31.440 --> 00:27:32.140
are generally

00:27:32.270 --> 00:27:34.420
for left-handed writers.

00:27:34.960 --> 00:27:36.220
Fan Jiangxue's painting

00:27:36.310 --> 00:27:37.900
used right-handed techniques.

00:27:38.590 --> 00:27:39.530
You mean

00:27:40.440 --> 00:27:41.730
the unsigned painting

00:27:42.000 --> 00:27:42.770
was painted by some

00:27:43.440 --> 00:27:44.290
left-handed person?

00:27:45.480 --> 00:27:46.380
Yes, exactly.

00:27:46.720 --> 00:27:47.380
Also,

00:27:47.510 --> 00:27:49.490
Fan Jiangxue's painting skills
were relatively immature,

00:27:49.960 --> 00:27:52.330
with a big gap compared to the painting

00:27:52.680 --> 00:27:53.620
signed by Hu Jie.

00:27:54.750 --> 00:27:56.090
Is it possible

00:27:56.440 --> 00:27:57.250
the unsigned one was

00:27:57.550 --> 00:27:58.380
also painted by Hu Jie?

00:27:58.590 --> 00:27:59.460
I'm not sure.

00:28:00.480 --> 00:28:01.730
But both Hu Jie's paintings

00:28:01.920 --> 00:28:03.490
and the unsigned one

00:28:03.790 --> 00:28:05.140
were painted using a reverse

00:28:05.160 --> 00:28:05.770
oblique nib.

00:28:06.350 --> 00:28:07.700
However, in terms of skill level,

00:28:07.720 --> 00:28:09.290
there's a clear gap between the two.

00:28:10.070 --> 00:28:11.660
Judging by painting technique,

00:28:12.550 --> 00:28:13.330
they are clearly not

00:28:13.880 --> 00:28:15.010
painted by the same person either.

00:28:15.830 --> 00:28:16.660
Instead,

00:28:17.400 --> 00:28:18.810
Hu Jie's paintings

00:28:19.000 --> 00:28:21.570
seem to be imitations

00:28:21.590 --> 00:28:23.380
of this unsigned painting.

00:28:25.200 --> 00:28:27.010
Okay, thank you.

00:28:27.350 --> 00:28:28.620
I'll consult you again if needed.

00:28:29.000 --> 00:28:29.660
Alright.

00:28:29.720 --> 00:28:30.730
I'll take my leave now.

00:28:35.310 --> 00:28:35.980
What do you think?

00:28:36.830 --> 00:28:37.900
Mr. Li only mentioned

00:28:37.920 --> 00:28:39.570
that Fan Jiangxue and Hu Jie

00:28:40.160 --> 00:28:41.660
used to meet often

00:28:41.750 --> 00:28:42.770
to paint on the mountain.

00:28:43.310 --> 00:28:44.090
But he didn't mention

00:28:44.110 --> 00:28:45.460
the existence of a third person.

00:28:46.030 --> 00:28:46.860
So,

00:28:47.590 --> 00:28:48.770
that third person

00:28:49.160 --> 00:28:50.220
must have only stayed

00:28:50.240 --> 00:28:51.420
briefly in Lijia Town.

00:28:52.070 --> 00:28:52.860
The locals

00:28:53.070 --> 00:28:54.420
didn't know of his existence.

00:28:54.920 --> 00:28:56.420
These three must know each other,

00:28:56.680 --> 00:28:58.220
and they met up

00:28:58.440 --> 00:28:59.570
to paint the same landscape.

00:29:03.000 --> 00:29:04.140
The fingerprint on this painting

00:29:04.160 --> 00:29:04.570
must have

00:29:04.590 --> 00:29:05.700
been left by the third person.

00:29:06.480 --> 00:29:08.140
He waited for Hu Jie to
return to the country

00:29:08.200 --> 00:29:09.290
and then killed her

00:29:10.030 --> 00:29:10.940
using the same method.

00:29:12.480 --> 00:29:13.460
I don't think it's like that.

00:29:13.920 --> 00:29:15.810
The weapon in both cases
was a fountain pen,

00:29:16.310 --> 00:29:17.220
but

00:29:17.510 --> 00:29:19.050
the perpetrator's methods
actually differed.

00:29:19.480 --> 00:29:19.940
Look,

00:29:20.880 --> 00:29:22.290
this is Hu Jie's wound.

00:29:22.790 --> 00:29:24.490
When the killer murdered Hu Jie,

00:29:24.960 --> 00:29:26.250
it was clean and precise.

00:29:26.350 --> 00:29:27.220
The pen tip

00:29:27.440 --> 00:29:29.250
accurately pierced the carotid artery

00:29:29.790 --> 00:29:31.050
without the slightest deviation.

00:29:31.400 --> 00:29:32.940
Now look at Fan Jiangxue's wound.

00:29:33.830 --> 00:29:34.700
This location

00:29:35.110 --> 00:29:37.620
is between the throat
and the carotid artery.

00:29:37.920 --> 00:29:39.980
And judging from the wound,

00:29:40.720 --> 00:29:41.330
it doesn't look

00:29:41.750 --> 00:29:43.490
like a direct pierce into the artery,

00:29:43.920 --> 00:29:44.660
more like

00:29:45.590 --> 00:29:46.220
a scratch.

00:29:48.240 --> 00:29:49.330
The killer targeted

00:29:49.400 --> 00:29:50.980
the carotid artery in both murders.

00:29:51.200 --> 00:29:52.570
Fourteen years later,

00:29:52.750 --> 00:29:54.290
the second killing was

00:29:54.310 --> 00:29:55.810
quicker and more precise than the first.

00:30:14.480 --> 00:30:14.940
Mr. Han,

00:30:16.000 --> 00:30:16.420
Mr. Qi,

00:30:16.590 --> 00:30:17.810
the hair from Fan Jiangxue's scene

00:30:17.880 --> 00:30:19.090
doesn't match Hu Jie's.

00:30:32.000 --> 00:30:32.460
Correct.

00:30:33.030 --> 00:30:34.420
Last Friday night,

00:30:34.590 --> 00:30:35.250
this lady

00:30:35.440 --> 00:30:36.570
did come to our restaurant

00:30:36.590 --> 00:30:37.050
for dinner.

00:30:38.000 --> 00:30:39.660
They sat at that table upstairs

00:30:39.960 --> 00:30:40.860
by the window.

00:30:42.200 --> 00:30:42.980
Why do you remember

00:30:43.000 --> 00:30:43.570
so clearly?

00:30:44.240 --> 00:30:45.660
Because she had

00:30:45.680 --> 00:30:46.810
a big argument with her friend.

00:30:47.160 --> 00:30:48.010
This lady

00:30:48.310 --> 00:30:49.620
even threw a drink at her friend,

00:30:50.070 --> 00:30:50.700
causing quite

00:30:50.920 --> 00:30:52.010
a commotion in the restaurant.

00:30:52.550 --> 00:30:53.220
Do you remember

00:30:53.240 --> 00:30:54.330
what the person she argued with

00:30:54.550 --> 00:30:55.290
looked like?

00:30:56.960 --> 00:30:57.660
It was a man.

00:30:57.920 --> 00:30:58.700
He wore a suit

00:30:58.960 --> 00:31:00.530
and looked quite refined.

00:31:05.350 --> 00:31:06.380
Can your surveillance cameras

00:31:06.880 --> 00:31:07.730
capture that area?

00:31:08.160 --> 00:31:08.570
Yes.

00:31:09.790 --> 00:31:10.530
Pull it up for me.

00:31:10.590 --> 00:31:10.940
Follow me.

00:31:15.000 --> 00:31:15.700
Can you fast-forward?

00:31:16.720 --> 00:31:17.090
Alright.

00:31:21.680 --> 00:31:22.290
Play from here.

00:31:27.110 --> 00:31:28.570
They were arguing so fiercely.

00:31:30.400 --> 00:31:31.330
Did anyone here hear

00:31:31.350 --> 00:31:32.530
what they were arguing about?

00:31:33.160 --> 00:31:34.980
Not sure.

00:31:35.400 --> 00:31:36.420
I wasn't here at the time.

00:31:38.440 --> 00:31:38.940
Can you help me

00:31:38.960 --> 00:31:40.330
copy this video footage?

00:31:40.960 --> 00:31:41.330
Sure.

00:31:42.070 --> 00:31:42.490
Thank you.

00:31:43.240 --> 00:31:43.530
Wang.

00:31:43.920 --> 00:31:44.220
On it.

00:31:53.200 --> 00:31:53.810
Hello, Mr. Han.

00:31:54.680 --> 00:31:55.490
We've found a suspect.

00:31:57.720 --> 00:31:59.050
We've traced this guy named Ruan Mingyu.

00:31:59.200 --> 00:32:00.770
He's Hu Jie's domestic art agent

00:32:01.240 --> 00:32:02.180
who sells her paintings.

00:32:05.920 --> 00:32:06.570
This

00:32:07.270 --> 00:32:08.330
is his studio.

00:32:22.000 --> 00:32:23.570
Hello, who are you?

00:32:38.110 --> 00:32:38.700
Hu Jie...

00:32:40.240 --> 00:32:41.180
she's really dead?

00:33:01.030 --> 00:33:01.620
So,

00:33:02.310 --> 00:33:03.490
the killer is left-handed.

00:33:04.160 --> 00:33:04.460
Correct.

00:33:04.960 --> 00:33:05.490
That was

00:33:05.880 --> 00:33:06.980
our judgment back then.

00:33:13.270 --> 00:33:13.770
We just had

00:33:13.790 --> 00:33:14.900
dinner a few days ago.

00:33:14.960 --> 00:33:15.620
I never thought...

00:33:18.790 --> 00:33:19.530
How did she die?

00:33:20.070 --> 00:33:21.290
After dinner,

00:33:21.680 --> 00:33:22.330
where did you go?

00:33:23.720 --> 00:33:24.380
After dinner,

00:33:24.750 --> 00:33:25.730
I came back here.

00:33:26.590 --> 00:33:27.570
This is my studio;

00:33:27.920 --> 00:33:28.810
I usually live here too.

00:33:34.920 --> 00:33:36.010
Can you tell us

00:33:36.550 --> 00:33:37.330
about the situation

00:33:37.880 --> 00:33:38.700
at dinner that day?

00:33:44.270 --> 00:33:44.810
We parted

00:33:45.640 --> 00:33:46.490
on bad terms that day.

00:33:47.110 --> 00:33:48.010
A buyer

00:33:48.720 --> 00:33:49.730
took a liking to a painting

00:33:49.750 --> 00:33:50.770
she did many years ago.

00:33:51.830 --> 00:33:53.140
I had negotiated the price for her,

00:33:53.830 --> 00:33:55.010
but she kept putting it off,

00:33:55.350 --> 00:33:56.220
refusing to give it to me.

00:33:56.640 --> 00:33:57.570
I finally managed

00:33:57.590 --> 00:33:58.420
to meet her that day,

00:33:58.880 --> 00:34:00.620
hoping to get the painting from her.

00:34:01.590 --> 00:34:02.570
But she regretted it again.

00:34:03.400 --> 00:34:04.180
Because of this,

00:34:04.790 --> 00:34:06.050
we had a small disagreement.

00:34:07.070 --> 00:34:07.770
Are you sure

00:34:08.440 --> 00:34:09.820
it was just a small disagreement?

00:34:19.590 --> 00:34:20.780
We did have

00:34:21.190 --> 00:34:22.090
quite an intense argument.

00:34:22.630 --> 00:34:23.380
Actually, it wasn't

00:34:23.400 --> 00:34:24.900
the first time Hu Jie went crazy.

00:34:25.440 --> 00:34:26.650
She was always

00:34:27.030 --> 00:34:28.090
a very emotional person.

00:34:29.150 --> 00:34:30.530
Sometimes she would shut herself

00:34:30.550 --> 00:34:31.420
away for no reason,

00:34:31.840 --> 00:34:33.170
not talking to anyone for a long time.

00:34:33.960 --> 00:34:35.170
Sometimes she was overly excited,

00:34:35.710 --> 00:34:36.570
painting for several days

00:34:36.590 --> 00:34:37.740
without eating or sleeping.

00:34:38.590 --> 00:34:39.340
In short,

00:34:39.800 --> 00:34:40.610
she was

00:34:41.110 --> 00:34:42.210
quite capricious.

00:34:43.480 --> 00:34:43.900
Are these all

00:34:43.920 --> 00:34:44.900
Hu Jie's paintings?

00:34:46.440 --> 00:34:46.980
Not all.

00:34:47.480 --> 00:34:48.490
Some belong to others.

00:34:49.070 --> 00:34:50.460
Before their paintings are sold,

00:34:50.480 --> 00:34:51.860
they are displayed here.

00:34:52.280 --> 00:34:53.860
You can think of this place

00:34:54.590 --> 00:34:56.210
as a display room.

00:34:57.440 --> 00:34:58.860
Can we look around?

00:35:00.590 --> 00:35:01.010
Please.

00:35:26.110 --> 00:35:26.610
By the way,

00:35:27.230 --> 00:35:28.170
do you know this person?

00:35:34.760 --> 00:35:35.420
No.

00:36:32.630 --> 00:36:33.690
Have you been to Lijia Town?

00:36:35.400 --> 00:36:35.820
Where?

00:36:39.760 --> 00:36:40.490
Lijia Town.

00:37:10.000 --> 00:37:11.170
This painting is priceless.

00:37:11.230 --> 00:37:13.380
Every decision I make is
for your own good.

00:37:13.440 --> 00:37:14.380
Can we not talk about this?

00:37:14.400 --> 00:37:15.340
It's really annoying!

00:37:15.400 --> 00:37:16.820
Are you crazy?

00:37:16.840 --> 00:37:17.900
The hair sample collected from

00:37:17.920 --> 00:37:20.050
Hu Jie's home matches
that of Ruan Mingyu.

00:37:20.110 --> 00:37:21.380
Let's not waste time here.

00:37:21.510 --> 00:37:22.210
Hu Jie's death

00:37:22.320 --> 00:37:23.610
has nothing to do with me.

00:37:23.670 --> 00:37:25.210
Song Weimin's sister
came to claim the body.

00:37:25.360 --> 00:37:26.340
When I sorted through

00:37:26.360 --> 00:37:27.340
his things the other day,

00:37:27.440 --> 00:37:28.900
I found he had left behind
a lot of drugs.

00:37:29.360 --> 00:37:30.690
This contest has been stopped for years.

00:37:30.920 --> 00:37:31.940
This is Hu Jie's Silver Award.

00:37:32.070 --> 00:37:32.690
Gold Award.

00:37:33.150 --> 00:37:33.940
Chen Chuchuan...

00:37:34.760 --> 00:37:35.690
What does he have to do with

00:37:35.710 --> 00:37:36.460
the Raw Diamond case?

00:37:36.670 --> 00:37:37.340
We are just one step

00:37:37.360 --> 00:37:39.090
away from the truth.

00:37:39.400 --> 00:37:39.900
Han Feng!

00:37:40.480 --> 00:37:41.460
You must stop here.